{
  "chapter": 32,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十二回 金大帅。梅汝男突然出现，郭大路和燕七惊讶不已。梅汝男透露她知道两人的目的，并提出一个大胆的计划：让郭大路从金家后园翻墙进入，假装欺负梅汝男，引出金大帅用连珠弹攻击他。若郭大路能接住连珠弹，就能成为小阔人；若接不住，则可能丧命。梅汝男借此要分三成利益。燕七虽表面冷淡，实则对郭大路心生情愫，在郭大路翻墙前轻声叮嘱，流露出深深的关切。郭大路最终同意冒险，燕七承诺会等他回来。章节末尾引出金大帅的登场，一个身材魁梧、气派非凡的武者。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我正想问你们，你们两个人怎么会跑到这里来的？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们在等你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么知道我会来？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我会算。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你呀，你说的话我连一个字也不信，因为你是个……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还在我娘肚子里时，已经常常到这里来玩了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们一定在打什么主意？我猜得对不对？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么我这个主意，也就不必说出来了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然你们并不是为此而来的，我说了也是白说。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们若是为此而来的呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么，我也许还能替你们出个主意，帮你们个忙。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但你的主意呢？你不说可不行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就知道你这个人从来不说老实话。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要怎么样你才肯说？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要有条件。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么条件？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来你想黑吃黑。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的主意若也不灵呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "灵不灵当场试验。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看你该改行去卖狗皮膏药才对。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这狗皮膏药你们买不实？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不买也是白不买。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不卖也是白不卖。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这就是金家的后门？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我就从这里跳墙进去，你要在后面追我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "然后呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "然后呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "然后呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若接不住呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那就说不定会变成一个死人了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我？我当然只能在旁看着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以无论我怎么样，你都连一点损失都没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然没有，否则我为什么要替你出主意？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "女人本就绝不肯做亏本的生意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "女人，唉，女人。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你究竟干不干？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不干也是白不干。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你死了可不能怨我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我若真死了，感激你还来不及，怎么会怨你？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "感激我？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "假的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "马马虎虎。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "马马虎虎是什么意思？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这在轻功的秘诀里有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就算撞破头我也会上去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你有把握能上得去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么法子？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就是这个法子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那只因为大多数男人都太笨。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你难道不是男人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是男人，可是我不笨。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还等什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我这一去，说不定真的会变成个死人，所以……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以怎么样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你现在总该将那个秘密告诉我了吧？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么还不行？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为这次你绝对死不了的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你有把握？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说你笨，你果然真笨。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你本来就笨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我哪点笨？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪点都笨，你为什么不能变得稍微聪明些呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我能不能不聪明？能不能笨一点？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是不是那很多女孩子其中之一？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不是，我也不敢。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
